{"tid":2371381,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史上會點樣評價IZONE？","createTime":"2021-01-18T21:05:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T03:41:28.000Z","uid":205928,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ef69018703ec874f348863f25369a3f64470298f","tid":2371381,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T21:05:42.000Z","msg":"2019年末因師弟團X1爆出造假風波<br />\n導致原定11月已釋出concept teaser既comeback Bloom*IZ被推遲 命運不明<br />\n<br />\n最後經紀公司決定在2020年二月重啟活動<br />\n以主打曲Fiesta comeback<br />\n為繼 La Vie en rose, Violeta後的以花為核心的第三部曲<br />\n<br />\nIZ*ONE的粉絲 WIZ*ONE們 為了向世界證明IZ*ONE的價值和證明他們對IZ*ONE的喜愛<br />\n交出了當時女團史上第一的銷量成績<br />\n以首周十七萬五千 及總銷量三十五萬<br />\n正式開創 歷史上稱為 &quot;女團2020年的銷量大增幅&quot;<br />\n&quot;The epic growth of sales of 4th gen girl groups in 2020&quot;<br />\n<br />\n而IZONE在同年也進行了兩次comeback<br />\n分別是 Oneric dairy 及 One reeler<br />\n銷量同樣驚人！ 合計三張專輯的年計總銷量超過百萬！<br />\n成為名符其實的百萬銷量女團！<br />\n<br />\n最終在2021年 原定活動期限結束前<br />\n對外宣布全員續約成功！<br />\n將繼續以IZ*ONE之外 活動至2024年10月！"},{"pid":"d3ef7dabb3603157196b5b7329c00545483a0ddb","tid":2371381,"uid":323450,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T21:20:39.000Z","msg":"永續IZ*ONE!!"},{"pid":"c320eeba6e681319b3eeedbd4f27bba0abaf25c2","tid":2371381,"uid":205928,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d3ef7dabb3603157196b5b7329c00545483a0ddb","tid":2371381,"uid":323450,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T21:20:39.000Z","msg":"永續IZ*ONE!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T21:21:21.000Z","msg":"永續IZ*ONE!! ㅠㅠㅠㅠ"},{"pid":"30bccd373c80d02fb1184d7452699be057713564","tid":2371381,"uid":118868,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T21:41:52.000Z","msg":"做馬加冇口齒<br />\n一係比返ioi黎先"},{"pid":"e2ce2a7575c7aa1960264212b4151d27f65cfcf1","tid":2371381,"uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30bccd373c80d02fb1184d7452699be057713564","tid":2371381,"uid":118868,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2